data.description: This is a one of a kind home - feels like a cozy bed-n-breakfast & perfect for multi-generational living. Kitchen has custom cabinets, granite counters & island, lg pantry; living rm has wd-burning frplce, beautiful wood flrs & lg windows to enjoy distant views; huge dining rm w/slate floors, wet bar & mini-frig (hook-ups for a 2nd kitchen); family rm is surrounded with view windows; 2-master suites; main master suite transports you to instant relaxation w/wd-burning fireplace, wd floors, luxurious master bath w/jetted tub, walk-in shower, granite counters & lg walk-in closet; office & much more. Detached 2 car workshop/garage. The home has custom ironwork details throughout. Multiple deck, hot tub. Private location, yet close to all conveniences. Many potential uses for this property.
